original:
Once upon a time in the small town of Pixelville, there lived a kid named Max. He woke up every morning excited for another day in a world that operated on video-game logic.
Max's day began as he hopped out of bed and slipped into his virtual reality suit. With a wave of his hand, his room transformed into a vibrant, neon-lit classroom. The teacher, Mrs. Pixel, awaited him with a cheerful smile. T
